longBusinessSummary: Xsovt Brands, Inc. operates as a footwear designer in the United States. The company engages in the design, comfort, and construction of shoes and slippers for men, women, and children. It sells its products under the Xsovt brand. The company was founded in 2004 and is based in North Las Vegas, Nevada.
